The scheme is being implemented in a mega-mission mode across Assam. CMSGUY will be implemented through a saturation model by covering each revenue village through focused interventions in direct economic activities, logistic support including market linkages, and community support. 
&lt;br&gt;

The scheme &amp;quot;Development of Playfield&amp;quot; is an Infrastructure Development Scheme by the Assam Youth Development Mission Society (AYDMS) formed under Chief Minister Samagra Gramya Unnayan Yojna (CMSGUY). AYDMS has decided to develop one playfield for the promotion of Games and Sports in the State through the Sports &amp;amp; Youth Welfare Department, Govt.
